{"tid":2269110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5年前痛失愛子　粗心媽又獨留女嬰在家害趴睡窒息死","createTime":"2020-11-03T09:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T09:40:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7508af05b4ab5c879f9ff89ef760a90e77c1e4","tid":2269110,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"今年7月新北市一名何姓婦人將3個月大的女兒獨留家中，3個小時後返家發現女嬰翻身俯臥，嘴巴、臉部嚴重發紫，立刻將她送醫急救，但女嬰仍因窒息夭折。新北地檢署查出何婦5年前才痛失次子，如今又照護疏失導致愛女喪命，今依過失致死罪將她起訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201103/5QBCREHCQJB6NCQYYD6GJVAF6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2F5QBCREHCQJB6NCQYYD6GJVAF6M%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=5529fc54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2F5QBCREHCQJB6NCQYYD6GJVAF6M%2F&h=58e669ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201103/5QBCREHCQJB6NCQYYD6GJVAF6M/</a>"},{"pid":"f58ea57dcf731ef39e22e3e4490fa9a3d38e5473","tid":2269110,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"窮人生"},{"pid":"0416adcc06b3e80e170aba8912b39ca3cca5dfd3","tid":2269110,"uid":210669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"好心咪撚生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f37934edc513b99bd6cae264ff68687bfee541d","tid":2269110,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285aa9c39ae711f8d5cb1e26e9ad753fbbbf40ee","tid":2269110,"uid":75610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:18:47.000Z","msg":"新北啲教育好唔撚掂喎"},{"pid":"1d7776b32de0bb708c4cc15929fca20bf791a6de","tid":2269110,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T09:22:35.000Z","ms